  "remarks": "\nAbdulvahap KOCAK is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 on the basis of the following ground: KOCAK is or has been involved in hostile activity by the Government of Iran, in that he has been responsible for threatening, planning or conducting attacks, including assassinations and threats to life, against persons in countries other than Iran.   \n",
